+## Overview
+
+Total revenue: $6,618.09. The dataset contains 30 orders across four regions spanning May 2–21, 2026.
+
+## Top Products
+
+Widget generated $1,459.26 in total revenue (36 units at $19.99 each), making it the highest-performing product. Gadget followed with $1,043.50, while Sprocket earned $828.75 and Doohickey $286.58.
+
+## Regional Performance
+
+North region produced $1,532.33 in revenue, followed by South ($1,579.25), East ($1,189.84), and West ($1,316.67). South led in total revenue despite having fewer orders, indicating higher average order values in that region.
+
+## Recommendations
+
+- Focus inventory on Widget and Gadget, which account for over 70% of total revenue from strong customer demand.
+- Investigate South region's higher average order value to identify patterns for replication across other regions.
+- Optimize Sprocket pricing or marketing; despite decent unit volume, it underperforms revenue-wise compared to other products.
